headline: UDR: Steady, High-Yielding, Well Managed, And Undervalued
summary: UDR Inc. (UDR) is a well-managed Apartment REIT offering a reliable 4.9% yield, trading at a 23% discount to fair value.

headline: UDR: A Turn Is Unlikely During 2026
summary: UDR faces weak rental conditions and excess supply, which are likely to delay material rental inflation until at least 2027. Find out why the stock is a Hold.
